OL,5,G2200 Best of Only an Excuse
OL,6,     F1/4. A special selection of
OL,7,     Fsketches picked from 27 years of
OL,8,     Fthe hit Scottish comedy. Tackling
OL,9,     FScottish football, mixing classic
OL,10,     Fcharacters, favourite skits and
OL,11,     Fhilarious media spoofs.
OL,12,G2230 Janey and Ashley Get a Real Job
OL,13,     F2/4. Comedians Janey Godley and
OL,14,     Fher daughter Ashley Storrie put in
OL,15,     Fsome hard graft on a construction
OL,16,     Fsite to prove they have what it
OL,17,     Ftakes to cut it outside the world
OL,18,     Fof comedy.
OL,19,G2300 Scotcast
OL,20,     FConversation about Scotland's
OL,21,     Fbiggest news stories, hosted by
OL,22,     FMartin Geissler.
